#: ../../source/user_guide/setting/authentication.rst:2
msgid "Authentication Management"
msgstr "认证管理"

#: ../../source/user_guide/setting/authentication.rst:4
msgid ""
"Loonflow supports multiple authentication methods. You can configure them"
" in the \"Setting\"-\"Authentication\" page. Currently, the supported "
"authentication methods are:"
msgstr "Loonflow中支持多种认证方式。你可以在\"设置\"-\"认证\"页面进行配置。目前支持的认证方式有："

#: ../../source/user_guide/setting/authentication.rst:6
msgid "Microsoft OIDC: Microsoft OIDC authentication."
msgstr "Microsoft OIDC: 微软OIDC认证。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/setting/authentication.rst:7
msgid "WeCom: WeCom authentication."
msgstr "企业微信: 企业微信认证。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/setting/authentication.rst:12
msgid "Microsoft OIDC authentication"
msgstr "微软OIDC认证"

#: ../../source/user_guide/setting/authentication.rst:13
msgid "Microsoft OIDC authentication is supported by Microsoft OIDC."
msgstr "微软OIDC认证由微软OIDC提供支持。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/setting/authentication.rst:15
msgid ""
"your need create a Microsoft OIDC app and get the client id, client "
"secret, redirect uri."
msgstr "你需要创建一个微软OIDC应用并获取客户端id，客户端密钥，重定向uri。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/setting/authentication.rst:16
msgid "create new microsoft oidc app"
msgstr "创建新微软OIDC应用"

#: ../../source/user_guide/setting/authentication.rst:21
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"add redirect url, your service must listen on https,and the redirect must"
" use be https://{your "
"domain}/api/v1.0/manage/auth/microsoft_oidc/callback"
msgstr "新增重定向URL，你的服务必须监听HTTPS，并且重定向必须使用HTTPS://{你的域名}/api/v1.0/manage/auth/microsoft_oidc/callback"

#: ../../source/user_guide/setting/authentication.rst:22
msgid "microsoft oidc redirect url"
msgstr "微软OIDC重定向地址"

#: ../../source/user_guide/setting/authentication.rst:29
msgid "WeCom authentication"
msgstr "企业微信认证"

#: ../../source/user_guide/setting/authentication.rst:30
msgid ""
"WeCom authentication is supported by WeCom. support use wecom scan QR "
"code to login."
msgstr "企业微信认证由企业微信支持，支持使用微信扫码登录"

#: ../../source/user_guide/setting/authentication.rst:32
msgid "your need create a wecom app and get the appid, agentid, redirect uri."
msgstr "你需要创建一个微软OIDC应用并获取客户端id，客户端密钥，重定向uri。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/setting/authentication.rst:33
#: ../../source/user_guide/setting/authentication.rst:39
msgid "create new wecom app"
msgstr "创建新的企业微信应用"

#: ../../source/user_guide/setting/authentication.rst:38
msgid "web app authorization configure"
msgstr "web应用授权配置"

#: ../../source/user_guide/setting/authentication.rst:44
msgid "add callback domain"
msgstr "新增重定向域名"

#: ../../source/user_guide/setting/authentication.rst:45
msgid "new wecom app callback domain"
msgstr "新企业微信应用回调域名"

#: ../../source/user_guide/setting/authentication.rst:50
msgid "add Company's Trusted IP"
msgstr "添加企业可信IP"

#: ../../source/user_guide/setting/authentication.rst:51
